@startuml
start
:The user opens the file browser;
if (Does the user want to use the GUI) then (Yes)
:The user searches for the file or folder;
:The user opens the context menu for the selected item;
:The user selects "Delete permanently";
:The system displays a confirmation dialog;
if (Does the user confirm deletion?) then (Yes)
:The system deletes the file or folder;
:The system removes the deleted item and its metadata from the graph;
else (No)
:The user cancels the operation;
endif
else (No)
:The user issues the DSL command to delete the file;
endif
stop
@enduml
